  "description": "<p>A field-proven, cold-weather bag for skiers and winter mountaineers who need warmth and compact volume. Sophisticated tailoring and copious 800-fill power goose down create a high-loft bag with concentrated warmth. The shell is a breathable laminate that sheds condensation to prevent the bag from gathering moisture or feeling damp. Its yoke and collar system completely encircles your neck to seal out drafts.</p><ul><li>Outer shell and the inside of hood is durable GORE-TEX\u00ae INFINIUM\u2122 WINDSTOPPER\u2122, a breathable laminate that provides exceptional wind and water resistance</li><li>Made with warm and light 800-fill power goose down that meets the Responsible Down Standard for animal welfare</li><li>Side block baffles control cold spots</li><li>2-way, \u00be-length zip doesn't add excess weight</li><li>Hood and shoulder drawcords have different profiles, so you can tell them apart in the dark</li><li>Roomy footbox gives feet plenty of space</li><li>Hanging loops at foot for storing or drying</li><li>Includes seam-taped, water-resistant, roll-top stuff sack and home storage cube</li></ul>",
